11. Find the complexity.
void fun(int n){
    if(n<=1) return;

    fun(n/2);
    fun(n/2);
}

Answer:

Recurrence:

T(n)=2T(n/2)+1

Complexity:

Θ(n)
12. Find the complexity.
void fun(int n){
    if(n<=1) return;

    fun(n-1);
    fun(n-1);
}

Answer:

Recurrence:

T(n)=2T(n−1)+1

Complexity:

Θ(2ⁿ)
