14. Maximum recursion depth?
void fun(int n){
    if(n==0) return;
    fun(n-1);
}

fun(100);

Answer:

101 stack frames

(including base call)

15. What is the output?
int fun(int n){
    if(n<=1)
        return 1;

    return fun(n-1)+fun(n-1);
}

cout<<fun(4);

Answer:

8
